{"tid":2455332,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋玉引玉] 嚴選一人N套冷冷哋門但睇完會好想其他人都一齊睇嘅漫畫作品","createTime":"2021-03-21T04:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T10:50:23.000Z","uid":229224,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3620828bda61aa55698c21c6c883bf06f03f1195","tid":2455332,"uid":229224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"如題，<br />\n<br />\n而家呢個世道大概就只有睇漫畫嘅時候大家先可以真真正正咁冷靜落嚟，忘記所有不快，而要做到呢樣嘢，就必須要有一個足以令你浸淫喺其中都不自覺嘅好漫畫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今日就嚟同大家推介兩套我覺得唔算太大眾（at least身邊無乜人會提起）嘅作品。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 噬謊者／嘘喰い／The Lie Eater<br />\n作者：迫稔雄／話數：539話／單行本數：49本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5x3K3MJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5x3K3MJ.jpg&h=18a648f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭以為只係 <em>超智遊戲</em> 之流嘅鬥智鬥力作品，啲作畫同文戲又有種令人尷鳩尬嘅感覺，但越睇落去越覺得不得了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過詳情就唔講了，有興趣自己睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨住故事嘅推進，就可以慢慢知道呢個世界觀嘅格局，有趣嘅就係佢好似 John Wick 咁，細得嚟，夠完整。亦都證明到故事嘅發展唔需要毫無意義地 expand，更加需要嘅係點到即止嘅收尾。（<em>七原罪</em>、<em>龍珠</em> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 怪物 MONSTER／モンスター／Monsutā<br />\n作者：浦澤直樹／單行本數：18本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdP2Qvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdP2Qvm.jpg&h=5d5a9b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>浦澤直樹</ins> a.k.a. <em>20世紀少年</em> 作者，呢套嘢有幾神相信唔洗我多講，而我介紹嘅呢一套我就覺得有過之而無不及。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先講缺點：一追呢套個人即刻無乜精神。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事關一睇就停唔閪到落嚟，用咗兩日時間一口氣 chur 撚哂，睡眠時間被打亂，返工都無力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢套分鏡同人物塑造力強，不過呢個係漫畫家嘅功力啦，而故事上營造嘅懸疑感好重，好引人入勝，令人好想繼續睇落去。<br />\n<br />\n越睇越有種心寒嘅 feel、成個人都會好沉重、代入感唔知點解咁重。（可能因為我係讀 History 嘅，而呢套嘢嘅故事背景係東西德糾紛時期嘅架空故事）總之就係好正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <del>唔好因為 title 叫 Monster 然後主角係天才腦外科醫生而覺得跟住落嚟係講個醫生整咗隻科學怪人出嚟，因為怪物，另有其人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先！唔想講劇情相關嘅嘢，因為想大家親自由零開始去接觸所有唔同嘅作品。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面大家接力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eb245331dd4499e33a74dfb19b84ffe64b4bd7","tid":2455332,"uid":229224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"毒撚開 post 無人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24690aa7c186e52b700a7edf38feb8928afc08a5","tid":2455332,"uid":200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:58:57.000Z","msg":"Happy Sugar Life<br />\nSola<br />\n奴隸兔"},{"pid":"26bcadbb74a4ff0b2d29fa7193da9301822e5b1b","tid":2455332,"uid":229224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"